    <description>
        <p>‚ú® Features</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Lightweight &amp; Fast ‚Äî No Electron!!</li>
            <li>Clean Interface ‚Äî Simple design with light and dark themes</li>
            <li>Cross-Platform ‚Äî Windows 10+, macOS 11+, Linux (AMD64, ARM64)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>üéÆ Game Management</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Grid View ‚Äî Browse games with cover art display</li>
            <li>Format Support ‚Äî .iso, .rvz and major formats via
                <code>NOD</code>
            </li>
            <li>Automatic Splitting ‚Äî .wbfs file splitting when needed</li>
            <li>Partition Stripping ‚Äî Remove unused partitions (experimental)</li>
            <li>Game Archiving ‚Äî Archive games using RVZ+zstd-19</li>
            <li>Integrity Checks ‚Äî Verify game data for corruption</li>
            <li>GameTDB ‚Äî Fetch covers and <code>wiitdb.xml</code> from GameTDB
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p>üõ†Ô∏è Wii Homebrew Management</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Apps View ‚Äî Manage Wii homebrew applications</li>
            <li>ZIP Import ‚Äî Add apps from <code>.zip</code> archives
            </li>
            <li>OSCWii ‚Äî Download apps from the Open Shop Channel</li>
            <li>Wiiload Transfer ‚Äî Send apps directly to Wii via network</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
